### Test Confirmation Letter API with Language Support

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5128
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Request Confirmation Letter in Vietnamese
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/service/confirmation-letter
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "Xin học bổng",
  "language": "vi"
}

### 2. Request Confirmation Letter in English
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/service/confirmation-letter
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "Apply for scholarship",
  "language": "en"
}

### 3. Request Confirmation Letter (Default Vietnamese)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/service/confirmation-letter
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "Xác nhận sinh viên",
  "language": "vi"
}

### 4. Get Confirmation Letter History (includes language)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/service/confirmation-letter/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

